                    <div class="mb-6 md:mb-8">
  <h2>Featured payments</h2>

  <div class="cards"><div><a href="/parental-leave-pay" class="card" data-lit-original-text="Parental Leave PaySupport to take time off work to care for a newborn or newly adopted child."><div class="card-content"><div class="card-title">Parental Leave Pay</div><div class="card-text"><p>Support to take time off work to care for a newborn or newly adopted child.</p></div></div></a></div><div><a href="/family-tax-benefit" class="card" data-lit-original-text="Family Tax BenefitA 2-part payment to help with the cost of raising children."><div class="card-content"><div class="card-title">Family Tax Benefit</div><div class="card-text"><p>A 2-part payment to help with the cost of raising children.</p></div></div></a></div><div><a href="/youth-allowance" class="card" data-lit-original-text="Youth AllowanceHelp if you’re under 25 and studying or training, or under 22 and looking for work."><div class="card-content"><div class="card-title">Youth Allowance</div><div class="card-text"><p>Help if you’re under 25 and studying or training, or under 22 and looking for work.</p></div></div></a></div><div><a href="/jobseeker-payment" class="card" data-lit-original-text="JobSeeker PaymentHelp if you’re between 22 and Age Pension age and looking for work."><div class="card-content"><div class="card-title">JobSeeker Payment</div><div class="card-text"><p>Help if you’re between 22 and Age Pension age and looking for work.</p></div></div></a></div><div><a href="/disability-support-pension" class="card" data-lit-original-text="Disability Support PensionHelp if you have a condition that is likely to last more than 2 years and meet the rules."><div class="card-content"><div class="card-title">Disability Support Pension</div><div class="card-text"><p>Help if you have a condition that is likely to last more than 2 years and meet the rules.</p></div></div></a></div><div><a href="/age-pension" class="card" data-lit-original-text="Age PensionIncome support if you’re Age Pension age and meet the rules."><div class="card-content"><div class="card-title">Age Pension</div><div class="card-text"><p>Income support if you’re Age Pension age and meet the rules.</p></div></div></a></div></div>
</div>

<div class="bg-blue-60 dark:bg-dark-blue-2-100 print:bg-white justify-center text-center py-9 px-6 -mx-6">
  <h2>More payments and services</h2>

